trans-unit.source: Confirms that a code assembly originates in the global assembly cache (GAC) as evidence for policy evaluation.
This class cannot be inherited.
The presence of <xref:System.Security.Policy.GacInstalled> evidence produces a <xref:System.Security.Permissions.GacIdentityPermission> in the grant set.
trans-unit.target: A presença de <xref:System.Security.Policy.GacInstalled> evidência produz um <xref:System.Security.Permissions.GacIdentityPermission> na concessão definido.

trans-unit.source: If there is a <xref:System.Security.CodeAccessPermission.Demand%2A> for <xref:System.Security.Permissions.GacIdentityPermission>, the <xref:System.Security.Permissions.GacIdentityPermission> that corresponds to the <xref:System.Security.Policy.GacInstalled> evidence is compared with the demanded permission.
trans-unit.target: Se houver um <xref:System.Security.CodeAccessPermission.Demand%2A> para <xref:System.Security.Permissions.GacIdentityPermission>, o <xref:System.Security.Permissions.GacIdentityPermission> que corresponde do <xref:System.Security.Policy.GacInstalled> evidência é comparada com a permissão exigida.

trans-unit.source: The object to compare with the current object.
Indicates whether the current object is equivalent to the specified object.
<see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="o" /> is a <see cref="T:System.Security.Policy.GacInstalled" /> object; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
<xref:System.Security.Policy.GacInstalled> objects have no properties to distinguish one from another, so all <xref:System.Security.Policy.GacInstalled> objects are equal.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Security.Policy.GacInstalled> objetos não têm nenhuma propriedade distinguir uma da outra, para que todos os <xref:System.Security.Policy.GacInstalled> objetos são iguais.
